criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  All patients from the Visceral Department of Basel University Hospital requiring open
             abdominal surgery. Open abdominal surgery is defined as: opened peritoneal cavity

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  factors limiting the ability to co-operate in the study;

          -  absence of signed informed consent before entering the study;

          -  people with mental disorders;

          -  pregnant women;

          -  participants under 18 years
